records.title: Springfield Battle Pass
records.content: Woo-hoo! Battle Pass holders this Season will instantly unlock the Peels Sidekick and get access to more premium rewards - including Simpsons Outfits.

records.author: Fortnite-API.com
records.title: Mixtape Music Pass
records.content: Unlock free and premium rewards in the Mixtape Music Pass by earning XP in any Fortnite experience. Purchase the Pass for only 1,400 V-Bucks or access it with Fortnite Crew to earn premium rewards. Music Pass holders instantly unlock the Sedona Outfit!

records.content: Small wings that create huge ripples across reality. Load into OG on November 8 before 2 PM ET to experience the dimension-warping effects of the butterfly!
